{"tid":651636,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"印度男看復仇者聯盟3當場死亡 摘下眼鏡雙眼仍睜開","createTime":"2018-05-03T08:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T09:16:07.000Z","uid":41453,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"815243cc9fcf5a2d587ba1ac60d3bb08dd03311d","tid":651636,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"印度媒體 <a href=\"http://timeofindia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeofindia.com&d=tvs6FLCP3kzxy%2BifI1j3NQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=2dd6a6d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">timeofindia.com</a> 今日報導，一名 43 歲的印度工人 Peddapasupula Baasha 於 5 月 2 日在戲院觀看《復仇者聯盟 3」、》時當場死亡，而死亡的時候並無任何跡象，法醫表示屬於自然死亡。<br />\n<br />\n《復仇者聯盟 3：無限之戰》全球掀起熱潮，印度也不例如，印度觀眾 Peddapasupula Baasha 一人前往印度的 Proddatur 戲院觀賞 3D 版《復仇者聯盟 3》，當散場的時候 Peddapasupula Baasha 仍坐在座位上一動不動，直到彩蛋也結束後，戲院工作人員試圖叫 Peddapasupula Baasha 卻沒有得到回應。工作人員隨後自行摘下 Peddapasupula Baasha 配戴的 3D 眼鏡，發現已經死亡，而且雙眼仍然睜開。<br />\n<br />\n由於 3D 電影需要配戴眼鏡，因此工作人員也無法即時判斷 Peddapasupula Baasha 是否身體有不適，而 Peddapasupula Baasha 死前一刻亦無任何異樣，工作人員表示散場的時候 Peddapasupula Baasha 仍坐在座位以為在等彩蛋，但彩蛋過後自行摘下 Peddapasupula Baasha 眼鏡才得知已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n初步判斷 Peddapasupula Baasha 為自然死亡、心臟停頓，等待醫院進一步的檢查。"},{"pid":"ebb25c6ed107e12e9d1ea856a56f76a397812c95","tid":651636,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"嚇死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7ae67e175586a53348fe549b2f92a322f52620","tid":651636,"uid":44243,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"佢代表印度一半人口犧牲左自己"},{"pid":"e711b7fe8bbf3d926a0cf945659296399a3a967c","tid":651636,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:48:18.000Z","msg":"嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c70d2c756ffc3